'''Pyrogrub''' is a {{Rarity|Rare}} fish found in the [[Roslit Bay#Roslit Volcano|Volcano]] in [[Roslit Bay]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Pyrogrub is a fearsome, lava swimming eel that thrives in the most volcanic of environments. The Pyrogrub sports thick dragon-like scales which allow it's inner body to not react to any form of outside temperature.|Bestiary Entry}}

